"{\"value\":{\"mdx\":\"### Query Transaction\\n\\nQuery the network for a transaction.\\n\\n#### Method Declaration\\n\\n:::code-group\\n\\n```python [Python]\\nasync def query_transaction(self, tx_hash: str) -> Tx\\n```\\n\\n```typescript [TypeScript]\\n\\n```\\n\\n```rust [Rust]\\npub async fn query_transaction(&mut self, tx_hash: &TxHash) -> Result<Tx, Error>\\n```\\n\\n```url [API]\\n\\n```\\n\\n:::\\n\\n:::details[Unification Plan]\\n:::\\n\\n#### Parameters\\n\\n| Parameter | Location | Type     | Description      |\\n| --------- | -------- | -------- | ---------------- |\\n| `tx_hash` | query    | [TxHash] | Transaction Hash |\\n\\n#### Response\\n\\n| Status | Meaning       | Schema | Description                              |\\n| ------ | ------------- | ------ | ---------------------------------------- |\\n| `200`  | [OK]          | [Tx]   | The response containing the transaction. |\\n| `400`  | [Bad Request] |        | The request was malformed or invalid.    |\\n| `404`  | [Not Found]   |        | The transaction was not found.           |\\n\\n[TxHash]: /types/tx_hash\\n[OK]: /types/ok\\n[Tx]: /types/tx\\n[Bad Request]: /types/bad-request\\n[Not Found]: /types/not-found\\n\",\"document\":[{\"href\":\"/node-client/public/query_transaction#query-transaction\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>Query the network for a transaction.</p>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/node-client/public/query_transaction.mdx#query-transaction\",\"isPage\":true,\"text\":\"\\nQuery the network for a transaction.\\n\",\"title\":\"Query Transaction\",\"titles\":[null,null]},{\"href\":\"/node-client/public/query_transaction#method-declaration\",\"html\":\"\\n<div class=\\\"code-group\\\"><div data-title=\\\"Python\\\"><pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\" data-title=\\\"Python\\\" data-lang=\\\"python\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#D